node.text: If you haven't tried @ACUVUE OASYS with Transitions™ yet, you're missing out. See how my eyes handle this Off The Field Challenge with my fave contacts 👀. See link in bio to get a free* trial pair of the contact lenses I've been wearing. Free trial lenses available from participating eye doctors. Exams and fitting fees not included. For safety info: http://bit.ly/2knQvyO

node.text: To the Grandparents, Parents, Sisters, Brothers, Aunts, Uncles, Cousins, Nieces, Nephews, and to all the people risking their life every day for something greater than themselves all over the Country, but especially the heroes in Philadelphia. You are loved and we thank you so much! Can’t wait to get back and help this City recover and have you all out at the Bank screaming and cheering us on! I love you guys!!💯

node.text: Where it all started..Happy Fathers Day to the greatest man I know! He taught me how to ride my bike, he let me be myself, he let me thrown the line even if we had to cut it, showed me what hard work means, and best of all made me feel the true love of a Father! I couldn’t ask for a better Pops to learn from each day. He’s the best dad, brother, uncle, grandpa, and friend around! I appreciate you and always will!! Pop a top and enjoy your day!🙌🏼 I love you!!
